TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: For data validations of 8-Day Menu Item Summary File.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: exp_8_day_mitm

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IS_NUMBER(v_NATL_STR_NU) AND IS_NUMBER(v_NON_CORP_ITM_CD) AND IS_NUMBER(v_SUM_TOT_SOLD) AND IS_NUMBER(v_SUM_WAS_SOLD) AND IS_NUMBER(v_SUM_PED_SOLD) AND IS_NUMBER(v_CNT_OF_DAYS) AND (TO_DECIMAL(v_CNT_OF_DAYS)>0 AND TO_DECIMAL(v_CNT_OF_DAYS)<100) AND IN (v_SRCE_OWSH_TYP_CD,'L','M') AND IS_DATE(v_MAX_DLY_SLS_DT,'MM/DD/YYYY') AND IS_DATE(v_RUN_DT,'MM/DD/YYYY') AND IS_NUMBER(v_COMBO_UNITS) AND IS_NUMBER(v_TOTAL_UNITS),1,0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: FLAG
